199
00:10:54,379 --> 00:10:56,200
We’re at a pub. We should have fun.

200
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,679
That’s enough, honey.

201
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:03,500
Are you that stressed out about your sister getting married?

202
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:04,879
