236
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:20,759
How can you say you’re okay when you’re so wasted? You’re not okay, Chef.

237
00:13:21,149 --> 00:13:24,990
I’m your mentor, Ting Nong Noy.

238
00:13:36,299 --> 00:13:36,679
Chef.

239
00:13:52,990 --> 00:13:54,320
