264
00:15:07,789 --> 00:15:08,720
Have some, Teacher.

265
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:12,669
My mother makes the best Thai tea almond cookies in the world.

266
00:15:13,679 --> 00:15:16,360
Can I try one of these then?

267
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,789
