Weir, I beg you.

294
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:52,829
Don’t touch me!

295
00:17:56,829 --> 00:17:58,170
Weir.

296
00:17:59,339 --> 00:18:02,119
Weir.

297
00:18:04,589 --> 00:18:06,559
