316
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,009
Talk to your mom.

317
00:20:16,799 --> 00:20:18,009
How are you, son?

318
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,339
I just want to talk to you.

319
00:20:25,069 --> 00:20:30,079
Weir, Mom just wants to apologize to you.

320
00:20:32,809 --> 00:20:34,079
Weir.

321
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,210
Weir,

322
00:21:07,740 --> 00:21:08,779
