324
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:16,619
You can’t run forever.

325
00:21:16,619 --> 00:21:18,759
But it’s no use talking to her.

326
00:21:22,730 --> 00:21:24,519
You of all people should understand

327
00:21:28,079 --> 00:21:30,200
