328
00:21:39,950 --> 00:21:40,400
Okay.

329
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:48,940
You can go out through the back entrance and take another day off.

330
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:27,710
I made Weir work too hard and he’s not feeling well,

331
00:22:28,589 --> 00:22:29,950
so I sent him home.

332
00:22:30,599 --> 00:22:34,140
I know Weir doesn’t want to see me.

333
00:22:34,859 --> 00:22:36,140
He must hate me a lot.

334
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:41,630
I cheated on my husband.

335
00:22:43,210 --> 00:22:44,119
Mom.

336
00:22:48,250 --> 00:22:49,180
It’s okay, View.

337
00:22:49,839 --> 00:22:52,960
It’s the truth and I’m ready to talk about it.

338
00:22:59,420 --> 00:23:02,940
I cheated on my husband and Weir saw it.

339
00:23:04,109 --> 00:23:06,490
I destroyed my family with my own hands.

340
00:23:07,319 --> 00:23:08,650
Most importantly,

341
