343
00:23:16,299 --> 00:23:16,990
Yes.

344
00:23:19,359 --> 00:23:23,480
I cheated on my husband with Weir’s first love.

345
00:23:24,599 --> 00:23:26,359
I’m a terrible mother.

346
00:23:27,519 --> 00:23:31,630
I made my son despise me so much that he’s too scared to get close to any girl.

347
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:40,430
But something good happened to Weir.

348
00:23:41,279 --> 00:23:43,609
These days, he’s very happy to be here with us.

349
00:23:45,609 --> 00:23:48,829
Thank you so much for hiring him.

350
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,359
No problem at all.

351
00:23:50,779 --> 00:23:52,920
You and view can rest assured

352
00:23:53,049 --> 00:23:55,920
that we take good care of Weir here.

353
00:23:57,079 --> 00:23:59,529
More like Chef is the one taking care of us.

354
00:24:00,910 --> 00:24:05,690
I’m glad that Weir got a job at a good place

355
00:24:05,869 --> 00:24:08,000
and has good friends who care about him.

356
00:24:08,829 --> 00:24:10,140
Thank you so much.

357
00:24:11,309 --> 00:24:13,160
Mom, you and View don’t have to worry.

358
00:24:13,660 --> 00:24:16,400
As a regular customer here,

359
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:21,799
I’m sure Weir will overcome his fear of women one day.

360
00:24:21,950 --> 00:24:23,900
There are no problems that can't be solved.

361
00:24:24,109 --> 00:24:25,000
I believe so.

362
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:27,769
