363
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,450
Shut up, Ting Nong Noy.

364
00:24:29,450 --> 00:24:31,450
Are you two dating?

365
00:24:31,450 --> 00:24:32,269
No.

366
00:24:34,619 --> 00:24:35,390
Mom,

367
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:37,599
